.SH NOTES
.IP \(bu 3
When
.B coolerdash
stops (during shutdown or reboot), it automatically displays the shutdown.png
image because sensor data is no longer available.
.IP \(bu 3
The CoolerControl service must be restarted after modifying
.I /etc/coolercontrol/plugins/coolerdash/config.ini
for changes to take effect.
.IP \(bu 3
Verbose logging (
.BR \-\-verbose )
is recommended when troubleshooting display issues or API communication problems.
.IP \(bu 3
Multiple instances of coolerdash cannot run simultaneously. The plugin is
automatically managed by CoolerControl.
.IP \(bu 3
The
.B \-\-force\-display\-circular
flag is deprecated. Use the
.B shape
configuration parameter instead for better control.
